Class EventHandlingController

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.istic.aoc.metronome.EventHandlingController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MEObserver, SliderObserver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockEventHandlingController

    public class EventHandlingController
extends java.lang.Object
implements MEObserver, SliderObserver
    Concrete controller class. This class has a observer role for the ME class and the Slider class.
    Author:
    Jiyoung Park.
    See Also:
    ME, Slider
